description: This is a short trivia game that will ask 5 questions about the Philadelphia Flyers. The user can respond with the answer to determine how much they know about the Flyers. If you are a true fan you will get 5 out of 5 questions correct.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, begin Flyers trivia and help
name: Flyers Trivia
shortDescription: Answer questions that will test your knowledge about the Philadelphia Flyers.
